^https?:\/\/mbd\.baidu\.com\/ccs\/v1\/start\/confsync\?appname=baidu_input reject-dict
^https:\/\/mime\.baidu\.com\/v5\/(fb\/st\?logtype|(notiv3|cellloc_noti|noti_cloudswitch_noti)\/info) reject-dict

